{{documentation subpage}}
<!-- EDIT TEMPLATE DOCUMENTATION BELOW THIS LINE -->
{{Main|Wikipedia:Avoid peacock terms}}
This tag provides a sleeker alternative for the {{Tl|Peacock}} tag, for inline use.
This tag will categorize tagged articles into [[:Category:Articles with peacock terms]] or a dated subcategory thereof.

== Usage ==
{{Tlx|Peacock inline|date{{=}}{{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}}}}

== Redirects ==
* {{Tl|Peacock-inline}}
* {{Tl|Peacock prose}}
* {{Tl|Peacock term}}

==TemplateData==
<templatedata>
{
	"params": {
		"date": {
			"autovalue": "May 2025",
			"suggested": true,
			"label": "Month and year"
		}
	},
	"format": "inline"
}
</templatedata>

== See also ==
* {{Tl|By whom}} &ndash; inline
* {{Tl|Peacock}} &ndash; message-box
* {{Tl|Weasel}} &ndash; message-box
* {{Tl|Weasel inline}} &ndash; inline
* {{Tl|Who}} &ndash; inline
== Redirects ==
{{list redirects|Template:Peacock inline}}

{{Inline tags}}

<includeonly>{{Sandbox other||
<!-- ADD CATEGORIES BELOW THIS LINE -->
[[Category:Inline cleanup templates]]

}}</includeonly>

